-team&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARichard+Huxtable\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20130512070917/http://cbme.nus.edu.sg/visit.html\">\"Visiting Staff &amp; Consultants\"</a>. National University of Singapore. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cbme.nus.edu.sg/visit.html\">the original</a> on 12 May 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 March</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Visiting+Staff+%26+Consultants&amp;rft.pub=National+University+of+Singapore&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcbme.nus.edu.sg%2Fvisit.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARichard+Huxtable\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ukcen.net/index.php/trustees\">\"Board of Trustees\"</a>. UK Clinical Ethics Network<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 March</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Board+of+Trustees&amp;rft.pub=UK+Clinical+Ethics+Network&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukcen.net%2Findex.php%2Ftrustees&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARichard+Huxtable\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink